00:34:45,380 --> 00:34:47,819
Chi-chi, Happy Chinese New Year!

438
00:34:47,819 --> 00:34:51,740
It's a brand new year, we'll play and get crazy together.

439
00:34:52,919 --> 00:34:54,436
Happy Chinese New Year, Lin Xichi!

440
00:34:54,436 --> 00:34:59,135
